data.description: Opportunity knocks with this unique property that offers 4 rental units on one tax lot! South Howard St offers two individual cottage style homes that are 3 bed/1 bath and 2 bed/1 bath, respectively. Additionally the main house is a split level duplex that offers two 1 bed/1 bath units. Nestled in the heart of Newberg, just blocks from George Fox University this property offers a world of possibilities to the 1st time landlord or savvy investor. Reserve your tour today!
